314
00:27:40,650 --> 00:27:42,310
Stop.

315
00:27:47,310 --> 00:27:48,970
Click.

316
00:27:50,470 --> 00:27:52,130
Click.

317
00:27:54,010 --> 00:27:55,790
Click.

318
00:27:56,550 --> 00:28:00,330
