365
00:32:28,670 --> 00:32:31,470
Do you know where Woo Ri Pharmacy is...?

366
00:32:34,090 --> 00:32:37,050
<i>I'll pack a delicious lunch and bring it to you.</i>

367
00:32:37,050 --> 00:32:41,650
<i>I'll come with the Thai style fried rice that you like.</i>

368
00:32:41,650 --> 00:32:43,750
<i>Please wait.</i>

369
00:32:49,990 --> 00:32:57,390
♫<i> That's all, you are the wind</i>♫

370
00:32:57,390 --> 00:33:03,170
♫<i> I'm a bird, that's all.</i>♫

371
00:33:04,770 --> 00:33:12,610
♫<i> That's all. You just come </i>♫

372
00:33:12,610 --> 00:33:17,530
♫<i> Then I fly away </i>♫

